            "content": "<p><strong>1. Is the Intimate Mist suitable for sensitive skin?</strong><br/><br/>Yes. Our Intimate Mist is gentle, hypoallergenic, and pH-balanced — making it safe for even the most sensitive skin.</p><p><strong>2. Does the Intimate Mist cause dryness, itchiness, or irritation?</strong><br/><br/>No. The mist is formulated to be extra gentle and non-irritating. It won’t cause dryness, itchiness, or discomfort when used as directed.</p><p><strong>3. Can I use the Intimate Mist every day?</strong><br/><br/>Absolutely. It’s designed for daily use and is gentle enough for repeated application.</p><p><strong>4. Are the fragrances safe for the intimate area?</strong><br/><br/>Yes. Our fragrance blends are alcohol-free, non-irritating, and have low sensitization potential — safe for the delicate intimate zone.</p><p><strong>5. Do I really need an intimate mist?</strong><br/><br/>If you want extra freshness, confidence, and a pleasant scent throughout the day, the Intimate Mist is a great addition to your routine. It’s made for external use only. If you prefer not to use a mist, you can always use the Intimate Wash on its own.</p>",
